        <item>
            <title>「微信保险」骗案新进展，警方拘捕上门收取骗款 15 岁男童</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/21/wechat-scam-2/tech-secure/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=wechat-scam-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/21/wechat-scam-2/tech-secure/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 12:00:33 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中热话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[资讯保安]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[微信保险]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[诈骗电话]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1257618</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">最近不少人都收到了骗徒冒充成微信客服的诈骗电话和短讯，警方最近就接获了一名 54 岁男子的报案，指自己遇到了「微信保险」骗案并被骗去 82 万和信用卡，最后更成功将骗徒拘捕。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">受害人当日收到了骗徒冒充成微信客服的电话，指他所申请的微信保险计划将每月自动扣费。他表示自己未有申请相关服务，骗徒声称可帮助他取消保险的自动扣账，并能安排同伙前往住所提供技术支援。受害人向骗徒透露住址，并将信用卡交给对方和把 82 万元转帐至骗徒户口，事后与家人交谈才意识到自己受骗并报案求助。警方翻查闭路电视片段和深入调查后，成功在黄大仙区以涉嫌「以欺骗手段取得财产」将当日上门收取骗款的 15 岁男童拘捕。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1257622 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/froala_687923114257-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/froala_687923114257-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/froala_687923114257.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.adcc.gov.hk/zh-hk/alerts-detail/alerts-1819277222420434945.html">反诈骗协调中心</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">警方指出最近「假冒客服」的骗案有上升趋势，呼吁市民提防受骗，切勿轻易交出个人资料和进行转帐，一旦怀疑受骗可致电 18222 至警方的「防骗易热线」。警方指「以欺骗手段取得财产」为严重罪行，最高刑罚为监禁十年，呼吁青少年勿因一时贪念而参与犯罪活动。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1257623 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/froala_79119493170-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/froala_79119493170-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/froala_79119493170.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1257624 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/froala_958737336644-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/froala_958737336644-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/froala_958737336644.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.adcc.gov.hk/zh-hk/alerts-detail/alerts-1819277222420434945.html">反诈骗协调中心</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2018468/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%A8%9B%E7%A8%B1WeChat%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%AE%A2%E6%9C%8D%E5%91%83%E8%B5%B082%E8%90%AC-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%8A%E9%96%80%E6%94%B6%E9%8C%A215%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5?fbclid=IwY2xjawEyhSdleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHQgdDAonXi46R-vEaQ5OhqtL6jww0rZHcz5m0A9rpYJXAnQK5tB0SxsSng_aem_yvgcoA5ir4ckEi-4c9CxoA">星岛</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1766684-20240819.htm">RTHK</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/08/wechat-scam/tech-secure/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">「微信保险」诈骗电话 Cut 线会打来问原因　连登网民分享对付骗徒新招</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/21/wechat-scam-2/tech-secure/">「微信保险」骗案新进展，警方拘捕上门收取骗款 15 岁男童</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
